[5] See Appendix I.

[6] George J. Romanes’s _Animal Intelligence_, 1^st ed. p. 233.

[7] Pierre Huber’s_ Les fourmis indigëes, Génève_, 1861; Forel’s _Recherches sur les fourmis de la Suisse, Zurich_, 1874, and J.T. Moggridge’s _Harvesting Ants and Trapdoor Spiders_, London, 1873 and 1874, ought to be in the hands of every boy and girl. See also: Blanchard’s _Métamorphoses des Insectes_, Paris, 1868; J.H. Fabre’s _Souvenirs entomologiques_, Paris, 1886; Ebrard’s_ Etudes des mœurs des fourmis, Génève_, 1864; Sir John Lubbock’s_ Ants, Bees, and Wasps_, and so on.

